title: FOXF Crosses Below Key Moving Average Level - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Tuesday, shares of Fox Factory Holding Corp (Symbol: FOXF) crossed below their 200 day moving average of $70.09, changing hands as low as $68.77 per share. Fox Factory Holding Corp shares are currently trading down about 3.3% on the day.
